{
  "2231190": {
    "name": "Magical Delicacy",
    "steam_appid": 2231190,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《魔法餐作室》是一款银河恶魔城风格的游戏，但比起紧张刺激的战斗，复杂的烹饪系统才是特色。进入格拉特小镇，<strong>通过在平台间跳跃来探索错综复杂的道路</strong>，找到通往未知区域的小径或者<strong>完成镇上居民各种具有挑战性的订单</strong>来推进游戏并解锁新的餐作用具。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >平台与探索是《魔法餐作室》的核心，你必须收集食材，推动游戏进程。如果想要更舒适的游玩体验，可以在设置当中降低游戏难度——当然，也可以主动让旅途变得更具挑战性！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231190/extras/8c0592bd8cc544fd09da3aef2cbe4410.poster.avif?t=1769018053\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231190/extras/8c0592bd8cc544fd09da3aef2cbe4410.webm?t=1769018053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231190/extras/8c0592bd8cc544fd09da3aef2cbe4410.mp4?t=1769018053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身小魔女弗洛拉，探索熙熙攘攘、人来人往的小镇。随心设计你的厨房，精心选择正确的原料，烹制可口的菜肴和神奇的药水。跳过一个又一个平台，往返镇上各处，结识镇上的居民，接收他们的订单，了解这个魔法世界。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >弗洛拉为了实现成为女巫的梦想，来到偏远的港口小镇格拉特，开了一间店。高崖之上的这个地方住了很多冒险家，他们来到这里都是为了探索尚未有人探索的神秘海岛，为了绘制海岛的地图。她经营店铺的时候，会遇到两个敌对女巫组织的成员。女巫卡西亚和法师塔乌诺可以教给弗洛拉很多东西，不过二人关于魔法存在各种分歧，也会利用弗洛拉对付彼此。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231190/extras/b6d08659837e9f89d232bab6a1b7b46d.poster.avif?t=1769018053\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231190/extras/b6d08659837e9f89d232bab6a1b7b46d.webm?t=1769018053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231190/extras/b6d08659837e9f89d232bab6a1b7b46d.mp4?t=1769018053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >走进美丽的港口小镇，邂逅形形色色的人，探索这里的历史，把握拓展业务的机会。<strong>在各路商人处采购</strong>，购买重要的物品和提升道具。<strong>接受各种订单</strong>，满足居民们对魔法美食的渴望。邂逅神秘的旅人、店主、被人遗忘的传奇和手艺高超的匠人，有些只在<strong>白天或者夜里</strong>出现。揭晓海岛与岛上神秘生物<strong>被人遗忘已久的秘密</strong>。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231190/extras/687e5d7026de3f38b351e2f0ba44ecaf.avif?t=1769018053\" width=616 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231190/extras/220887ed78b839c0464bf09b27636790.poster.avif?t=1769018053\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231190/extras/220887ed78b839c0464bf09b27636790.webm?t=1769018053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231190/extras/220887ed78b839c0464bf09b27636790.mp4?t=1769018053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>资源管理</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要为顾客烹饪美味，正确的食材是不可或缺的。 你可以从鲜有人注意到的角落直接<strong>采集食材</strong> ，但有些食材只能<strong>直接从商人处购买</strong>。在烹饪的时候发现食材不足了？别担心，商人会重新进货，一些自然食材在采集后也会重新生长。升级你的厨房来储存食材，以便烹饪或实验，又或者将食材卖给商人来换取珠子——这可是用来交易的宝贵货币。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231190/extras/3e31fa543c70787f2ed3da1f41a5df8b.avif?t=1769018053\" width=616 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231190/extras/566079e1e055c76749d93fce53f2ab61.poster.avif?t=1769018053\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231190/extras/566079e1e055c76749d93fce53f2ab61.webm?t=1769018053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231190/extras/566079e1e055c76749d93fce53f2ab61.mp4?t=1769018053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>烹饪</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用<strong>获取的食材</strong>制作魔法菜肴，其不同的属性会需要你做出不同的搭配选择。<strong>发现并学习</strong> 不同口味融合之后产生的奇妙反应，满足不同的客人对食物的要求。<strong>严格遵照食谱的说明或者自己进行创造</strong>，然后把你的药水、餐品、茶饮和糕点<strong>卖给或者送到</strong>朋友和客人手上。镇上有呱呱叫的加保，也有身轻如猫的缇林，不论是本地的餐品还是弗洛拉家乡的特产，只要可以满足他们的味蕾就行。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231190/extras/3b5e7ff0e6fa45e355b3e4639fe0864a.avif?t=1769018053\" width=616 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231190/extras/f6a33a9e6233e114f57f3395df4ba524.poster.avif?t=1769018053\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231190/extras/f6a33a9e6233e114f57f3395df4ba524.webm?t=1769018053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231190/extras/f6a33a9e6233e114f57f3395df4ba524.mp4?t=1769018053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>经营店铺</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开局只有基本的装备，但是<strong>可以获得新的厨具</strong>。不断扩大厨房空间，根据自己的喜好放置厨具，以便充分提高烹饪的工作效率。把用不着的东西拿出来出售，把材料分好类存储，还能<strong>在后院种一些植物</strong>。要不是有一个不请自来的室友和经济方面的焦虑，这里完全可以说是你的一片梦想中的天地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231190/extras/a0ef64eaecba40bf1b63c5fb1166bd01.avif?t=1769018053\" width=616 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231190/extras/99d969d94c07dd73492f0668daaa82b5.poster.avif?t=1769018053\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231190/extras/99d969d94c07dd73492f0668daaa82b5.webm?t=1769018053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231190/extras/99d969d94c07dd73492f0668daaa82b5.mp4?t=1769018053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>平台移动</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >送货期间穿行于镇上各处，攀爬钟楼和旧城墙，或者在地下墓穴中探险。不断成长，不断<strong>提升你的移动能力</strong>，就能发现新的路线，到达原本无法前往的地方，或者发现回店的近路。发现地图上隐藏的蜿蜒小路并记住每一位镇上居民的位置。游戏受了银河恶魔城类别的启发，将相关元素浓缩成了一款温馨的烹饪游戏。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231190/extras/e8a210f5e625230d8acd57b66b1b7a84.avif?t=1769018053\" width=616 height=96 /></span><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 独特的<strong>像素美术</strong>画风，描绘了魔法小镇的奇妙与精彩。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结识<strong>形色各异的角色</strong>，向他们供应餐品。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2D平台游戏</strong>，受各类银河城作品启发。获得新的能力，到达新的地方，解锁新的近路。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >学习<strong>涵盖广泛的烹饪系统</strong>，发挥你的创意，满足客人特别确切的奇怪需求。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过交易、任务和探索获得新的食谱和<strong>食材</strong>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >推进线索交织的<strong>情节</strong>依赖对地图的探索以及不断完成订单。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>线性剧情</strong>，选择性遭遇事件和自由探索机会众多，开放式的结局。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大量<strong>辅助功能</strong>，方便玩家根据自己的情况调节游戏体验，包括“降低平台行动难度”的模式。</p></li></ul>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 德语, 日语, 简体中文, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 繁体中文",
